1
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:08,192
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,320 --> 00:01:11,232
=Episode 9=

3
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,696
Mother has been wary
of military officials.

4
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:29,040
And she has indeed warned me
to remain vigilant.

5
00:01:30,519 --> 00:01:31,400
But I will not...

6
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:31,920
So,

7
00:01:34,879 --> 00:01:36,120
you were aware of it?

8
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:38,680
No, not like that.

9
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:41,120
About the incense...

10
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:41,799
Enough.

11
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:46,879
Your Majesty always has reasons
for everything you do.

12
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:12,879
Xu Yu.

13
00:02:18,719 --> 00:02:20,840
I am currently physically weak.

14
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:23,639
I beg Your Majesty

15
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:25,840
to be considerate of me.

16
00:02:29,919 --> 00:02:31,199
(Xiao Jinyun,)

17
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:34,360
(I wish it was a misunderstanding.)

18
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,199
Xu Yu.

19
00:02:40,639 --> 00:02:41,599
(Xu Yu.)

20
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,360
(How can I make you understand)

21
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,280
(that I will never hurt you?)

22
00:02:52,479 --> 00:02:53,280
Mother.

23
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:56,120
You put too much incense

24
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:58,599
in Xu Yu's palace.

25
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,960
You already know it?

26
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:03,280
Yes, it was my doing.

27
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,759
Mother.

28
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,719
Do you despise Xu Yu that much?

29
00:03:08,919 --> 00:03:11,240
To the point of preventing her
from conceiving?

30
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,800
Wasn't that Your Majesty's intention?

31
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:18,280
(It truly was Xiao Jinyun's idea.)

32
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:21,400
You feared her family's growing power.

33
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:24,840
As your mother,
I naturally do something for you

34
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,759
to make you avoid getting involved.

35
00:03:35,159 --> 00:03:36,280
Stop doing it from now on.

36
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:39,360
After all, I don't like Xu Yu.

37
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:44,159
Jinyun.

38
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:54,240
The border is unstable,
and Dada is stirring.

39
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,840
War may be imminent.

40
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:57,000
Your Majesty.

41
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:59,800
This matter should be discussed
with the ministers.

42
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,240
I know nothing of that.

43
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,560
If Your Majesty is unwell,

44
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,840
you should return and rest.

45
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:14,120
Xu Yu probably doesn't wish
to see me right now.

46
00:04:15,319 --> 00:04:17,759
Tonight, I shall stay here.

47
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:18,759
Your Majesty.

48
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,199
I can watch celestial signs,

49
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:23,399
but I cannot manage marital disputes.

50
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,720
Who asked you to manage that?

51
00:04:26,319 --> 00:04:28,319
I want to switch our bodies back
immediately.

52
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,519
With war looming on the horizon,

53
00:04:30,519 --> 00:04:33,079
I can't let Xu Yu bear all the pressure.

54
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,519
Your Majesty.

55
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,720
I have found a way
to switch your bodies back.

56
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:43,759
I only need
to draw an identical Yin-Yang Talisman.

57
00:04:44,439 --> 00:04:45,759
But drawing this talisman

58
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:50,079
requires the sacred Soul Silk
from Dada to be effective.

59
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:56,839
We cannot request this item
directly from Dada,

60
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:59,120
or Tao Kan and his men
will become suspicious.

61
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,800
Unnecessary complications would arise.

62
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:04,920
Grand Preceptor,
you must not speak of this to anyone,

63
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,240
including Xu Yu.

64
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:15,959
Your Majesty,
weren't you staying here tonight?

65
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:19,040
It's time for Xu Yu
to take her medicine.

66
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,680
Am I truly so unwelcome?

67
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:55,776
I won't disturb Your Majesty
while you're reviewing memorials

68
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:59,519
in case you will bring your wrath
upon my father and brothers.

69
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:02,680
So is this how you see me?

70
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,079
Xu Yu.

71
00:06:09,879 --> 00:06:11,839
We have been through so much together.

72
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:16,639
Why can't you
have even a little trust in me?

73
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,720
These memorials still await your review.

74
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,639
Please focus on your duty, Your Majesty.

75
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:23,879
I'll take my leave.

76
00:06:27,104 --> 00:06:32,519
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

77
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,800
Sit next to me.

78
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:39,120
I don't want others to think
we are at odds again.

79
00:06:40,079 --> 00:06:41,240
It's to avoid suspicion.

80
00:06:46,839 --> 00:06:48,000
Tao Kan is quite alert.

81
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:52,240
Right after Lady Tao was in trouble,
he requested to cut ties with her.

82
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:55,839
Using witchcraft is a capital offense.

83
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:59,680
It's reasonable for him to do that.

84
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:02,800
He claimed
that Lady Tao wasn't his real niece.

85
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:05,959
The real one died long ago
on her journey to find her family.

86
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,160
He wants to sever all connections.

87
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,839
The one he sent in was a fake one
from the beginning.

88
00:07:12,079 --> 00:07:13,000
Once we find out,

89
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:16,600
he plays the victim,
claiming he was deceived.

90
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,480
You knew all along?

91
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:23,360
Most concubine candidates
they sent were their spies.

92
00:07:24,079 --> 00:07:24,959
I have to be wary.

93
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,000
Right.

94
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,000
Your Majesty is so wise.

95
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:32,720
We've been under your control
since entering the palace.

96
00:07:36,759 --> 00:07:38,199
I don't guard against everyone.

97
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:41,839
Sure.

98
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:45,199
But you're very wary of daughters
from military families.

99
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:49,040
Fine, Xu Yu.

100
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:51,240
If you insist on judging me this way,

101
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,959
I shall grant your wish then.

102
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:12,199
As the Empress,
you always treat me with indifference.

103
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,519
That is quite disrespectful.

104
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,639
If people hear

105
00:08:15,839 --> 00:08:18,480
that you argue with me
and then accidentally hurt me,

106
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:21,408
what do you think
will happen to your father and brothers?

107
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:23,720
You're despicable.

108
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:26,720
If you can just obey willingly,

109
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,759
stay by my side, and even smile at me,

110
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,439
what does it matter if I'm despicable?

111
00:08:31,488 --> 00:08:35,104
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

112
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:39,240
It's not that I can't be despicable.

113
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,799
I just don't want
to be despicable to you.

114
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:47,136
♪All who believed love would never fade♪

115
00:08:47,635 --> 00:08:52,397
♪The wind scatters countless sorrows♪

116
00:08:52,768 --> 00:08:55,039
♪Like a song, like a dream, like a play♪

117
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:56,240
May I get up now?

118
00:08:58,832 --> 00:09:04,586
♪No one ferries me
across this sea of pain♪

119
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:09,200
Shall we just sit here
quietly like this?

120
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,000
Your Highness.

121
00:09:42,159 --> 00:09:44,840
Aren't you supposed to go undercover
in Dada to find the Soul Silk?

122
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:47,240
Why do you keep lingering in my place?

123
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:49,519
Jinyun ordered me
to watch Tao Kan and his men.

124
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,600
But Tao Kan has become careful.

125
00:09:51,879 --> 00:09:53,279
He has been staying home recently.

126
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:55,559
He doesn't even drink outside anymore.

127
00:09:57,480 --> 00:10:00,720
He must've been terrified
by my commanding presence last time.

128
00:10:02,639 --> 00:10:03,480
Your Highness.

129
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:06,440
Won't you reconcile His Majesty
and Her Majesty?

130
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,679
Don't worry.

131
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,960
I'm sure

132
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,960
I can make it happen.

133
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:17,240
Well then,

134
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:20,600
I truly have nothing left to say.

135
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:22,639
You could praise my brilliance.

136
00:10:22,639 --> 00:10:23,440
Or you could...

137
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,039
Your Highness.

138
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:27,039
State affairs should
be our priority now.

139
00:10:34,379 --> 00:10:34,879
Xu Yu.

140
00:10:34,879 --> 00:10:35,720
- Have some tea.
- No, thanks.

141
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:38,519
If you're going to speak a good word
for Xiao Jinyun,

142
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:39,679
no need to speak then.

143
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:40,759
Xu Yu.

144
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:42,799
You clearly know why I see you today.

145
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,440
Yet you still came, didn't you?

146
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:47,840
I merely accepted your invitation
for an outing outside the palace.

147
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:49,480
Besides, you're a prince.

148
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,919
How could I dare refuse you?

149
00:10:50,919 --> 00:10:52,000
Please, Xu Yu.

150
00:10:52,559 --> 00:10:54,360
You can't blame me indiscriminately

151
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:56,639
just because Jinyun hurt you.

152
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,840
So, you do know

153
00:10:59,039 --> 00:10:59,879
that he hurt me?

154
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:00,620
No.

155
00:11:01,399 --> 00:11:03,080
Jinyun's feelings for you

156
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,759
can be witnessed by the sun and moon.

157
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:09,320
Unfortunately,

158
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:12,240
today is overcast
with no sun and moon in sight.

159
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,559
Well, his feelings
can be witnessed by the clouds.

160
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:19,960
Xu Yu.

161
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:23,559
Aren't you curious about Jinyun's past?

162
00:11:23,879 --> 00:11:24,399
No.

163
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,159
But what if I tell you

164
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,840
that he's afraid
to show his affection for you?

165
00:11:32,759 --> 00:11:33,720
What do you mean?

166
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:36,559
When Jinyun was 15,
he wanted a tortoiseshell cat.

167
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:39,120
Corrupt officials
used this as a pretext for plunder.

168
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:40,960
Among them was Mudan's father.

169
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,120
He wanted to occupy a village's land,

170
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:45,639
so he said the village hid the cat
and refused to surrender it.

171
00:11:45,639 --> 00:11:47,080
He then massacred the village.

172
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:50,960
When the premium tortoiseshell cat
was finally found later

173
00:11:51,159 --> 00:11:52,279
and presented to Jinyun

174
00:11:52,279 --> 00:11:54,559
through multiple officials,
it was already dead.

175
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:57,519
I did hear about that.

176
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:02,399
Moreover, Xiao Jinyun left the capital
for a time because of it.

177
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:07,000
Later, Jinyun personally requested
to investigate this case

178
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,720
and arrested corrupt officials.

179
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,159
But since then,

180
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:12,440
Jinyun has never dared
to show his preferences.

181
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:14,960
His feelings for you
have been hidden even deeper.

182
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,759
To gift you that greenhouse,

183
00:12:16,759 --> 00:12:19,159
he had to invent numerous excuses

184
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,840
just to silence the ministers.

185
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:22,840
He managed to hide his real intention.

186
00:12:24,679 --> 00:12:27,679
Besides this, Jinyun has another secret.

187
00:12:30,799 --> 00:12:31,480
Come closer.

188
00:12:34,559 --> 00:12:37,159
It's hidden in the box
on the bottom shelf of his study.

189
00:13:04,159 --> 00:13:04,840
Grapes?

190
00:13:05,279 --> 00:13:08,120
Your Majesty,
don't you dislike grapes most?

191
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,960
Why deliver them then?

192
00:13:14,399 --> 00:13:15,519
Your Majesty,

193
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:17,639
these grapes
are specially for Her Majesty.

194
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:20,519
You worried others might exploit this,

195
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:22,799
so whenever tribute grapes arrive,

196
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:24,240
they're first brought to you.

197
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:27,200
After you pretend to eat some,
they're distributed to others.

198
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:30,639
But only Her Majesty
receives grapes of the finest quality.

199
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:32,440
Grapes!

200
00:13:40,879 --> 00:13:41,840
Quite sweet.

201
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:44,200
The tribute grapes are so delicious!

202
00:13:44,879 --> 00:13:47,960
I truly hope His Majesty bestows gifts
upon the harem every day.

203
00:13:58,159 --> 00:14:00,080
(I thought he liked grapes.)

204
00:14:00,919 --> 00:14:02,639
(Turns out it was because I like them.)

205
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:15,320
(They're just grapes.
I don't have to eat them.)

206
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,399
(Jinyun has another secret.)

207
00:14:17,679 --> 00:14:20,480
(It's hidden in the box
on the bottom shelf of his study.)

208
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:24,799
By the way, bring me the box
on the bottom shelf of the cabinet.

209
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:25,600
Yes.

210
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:42,559
You've always wanted
to return this wooden comb.

211
00:14:42,799 --> 00:14:44,960
Because of that,
you even caught a cold for days.

212
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:46,080
I fell ill?

213
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:48,200
Back then,
the Empress Dowager scolded you,

214
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:50,320
saying you always defended Her Majesty

215
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:53,200
so that Her Majesty
neglected the management of the harem.

216
00:14:53,639 --> 00:14:56,159
Back then, you also wanted
to persuade Her Majesty.

217
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:58,639
But somehow you ended up arguing

218
00:14:58,799 --> 00:15:00,320
and even breaking the wooden comb.

219
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:04,960
Your Majesty gave me this.

220
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,799
At that time, I thought,

221
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:09,480
that having grown up together,
we'd also grow old together.

222
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,679
Now, I give it back.

223
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:14,919
I hope Your Majesty will give it
to the right head of the harem.

224
00:15:16,039 --> 00:15:17,120
I give up.

225
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:27,639
(At first, I thought Xiao Jinyun
was helping Consort Zhao to scold me.)

226
00:15:28,039 --> 00:15:29,000
(So I got angry.)

227
00:15:29,759 --> 00:15:33,000
(I never thought he would come
in the rain to return the comb.)

228
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:35,279
(But I misunderstood.)

229
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:38,720
Later, you wanted
to return the wooden comb.

230
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:42,159
But when you reached the Fengyi Palace,
you were driven back by the heavy rain.

231
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:42,919
After that...

232
00:15:42,919 --> 00:15:43,919
Enough, stop talking.

233
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:47,360
What about this wooden comb?

234
00:15:50,039 --> 00:15:50,799
Keep it.

235
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:52,679
Yes.

236
00:15:55,639 --> 00:15:56,480
(Ledger of the 4th Year of Jing'an)
What is this?

237
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:59,480
This is the account book
you prepared for Her Majesty.

238
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:01,120
The Empress Dowager

239
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:03,480
(Expense records)
wanted to test Her Majesty's skills.

240
00:16:03,879 --> 00:16:06,240
For fear that Her Majesty
would be punished,

241
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:08,320
Your Majesty kept the accounts
and had them copied.

242
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,639
No offense,

243
00:16:10,879 --> 00:16:12,519
but Your Majesty
has quietly done so much.

244
00:16:12,519 --> 00:16:16,200
If Her Majesty doesn't know,
how can she know you care about her?

245
00:16:17,279 --> 00:16:20,159
(No wonder I never got punished
every time the Empress Dowager)

246
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,720
(checked the account books.)

247
00:16:22,039 --> 00:16:25,399
(Turns out the account books
had been swapped all along.)

248
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:30,720
What else have I done for the Empress?

249
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,480
The greenhouse, Your Majesty.

250
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:35,080
That was something you did personally
under pressure.

251
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,360
You may leave now.

252
00:16:38,919 --> 00:16:39,559
Yes.

253
00:16:46,159 --> 00:16:48,799
(Turns out you've quietly done so much
for me.)

254
00:16:49,679 --> 00:16:51,919
(Yet I didn't dare
to open my heart to you.)

255
00:16:52,799 --> 00:16:54,519
(Nor did I dare to truly trust you.)

256
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,320
(Xiao Jinyun.)

257
00:16:58,200 --> 00:16:59,559
(I really miss you.)

258
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,320
(I want to see you.)

259
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:04,039
(There are so many misunderstandings
between us.)

260
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:30,464
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

261
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:35,763
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

262
00:17:37,088 --> 00:17:42,503
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

263
00:17:43,072 --> 00:17:47,616
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

264
00:17:48,256 --> 00:17:53,520
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

265
00:17:53,888 --> 00:17:59,565
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

266
00:17:59,904 --> 00:18:01,920
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

267
00:18:02,112 --> 00:18:05,856
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

268
00:18:06,432 --> 00:18:11,104
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

269
00:18:11,648 --> 00:18:13,408
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

270
00:18:13,728 --> 00:18:17,344
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

271
00:18:17,591 --> 00:18:23,118
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
